VWith a view to promoting the songs of saint composer Annamacharya, PNS Enterprises (52168865) has released Sri Rama, an album containing ten songs of the poet.A highlight is that the album contains the lyrics with notations that can be viewed on the monitor even as the songs rendered by G. Nageswara Naidu, asthana vidwan of Tirumala Tirupati Devasthanam, Andhra Pradesh, gives aural pleasure. The ragas have been selected to suit the bhava of the composition.The notations, which can be accessed by opening a folder, in English, Tamil and Telugu, can be downloaded.Bottom Template Starts
